Because there is no platform digital trustless value transfer that will ensure that we both get what we want: Me getting the money, and you getting the shares.</span></span></span></a><span key="196cfaafe9be41dcb42704e6c25a2aae"><span offset-key="196cfaafe9be41dcb42704e6c25a2aae:0"><span slate-zero-width="z">â€‹</span></span></span>
